#. translators: Label in event details row.
msgid "Tickets:"
msgstr "Tickets:"

#. translators: Shown when event is sold out.
msgid "Sold Out"
msgstr "Ausverkauft"

#. translators: %s: Number of tickets remaining.
msgid "%s remaining"
msgstr "%s verfügbar"

#. translators: %s: Number of attendees registered.
msgid "%s registered"
msgstr "%s angemeldet"

#. translators: Shown when capacity is unlimited and nobody has registered yet.
msgid "Tickets Available"
msgstr "Tickets verfügbar"

#. translators: ARIA label for the progress bar.
msgid "Ticket availability"
msgstr "Ticketverfügbarkeit"

#. translators: Shown when all remaining tickets are already in the cart.
msgid "Sorry, there are no more tickets available for this event."
msgstr "Leider sind für diese Veranstaltung keine Tickets mehr verfügbar."

#. translators: 1: total remaining, 2: quantity already in cart.
msgid "Sorry, only %1$s ticket(s) remaining for this event. You already have %2$s in your cart."
msgstr "Leider sind nur noch %1$s Ticket(s) für diese Veranstaltung verfügbar. Du hast bereits %2$s in deinem Warenkorb."

#. translators: %s: number of tickets remaining.
msgid "Sorry, only %s ticket(s) remaining for this event."
msgstr "Leider sind nur noch %s Ticket(s) für diese Veranstaltung verfügbar."

#. translators: %s: number of tickets remaining.
msgid "Cart quantity was adjusted. Only %s ticket(s) remain for this event."
msgstr "Die Menge im Warenkorb wurde angepasst. Es sind nur noch %s Ticket(s) für diese Veranstaltung verfügbar."

#. translators: Shown when cart ticket item is removed because event sold out.
msgid "This event is sold out. The ticket was removed from your cart."
msgstr "Diese Veranstaltung ist ausverkauft. Das Ticket wurde aus deinem Warenkorb entfernt."
